        args='{"prompt":"In {{spacex_s1}}, what is the segment reporting policy? How is segment income from operations defined? What costs are allocated to segments vs. corporate? Include any discussion of how depreciation, manufacturing costs, and capital expenditures are allocated to the AI segment."}',
